Ques.1: Find the number of movies each director has directed.
Query : SELECT director, COUNT(*) AS num_movies
        FROM movies
        GROUP BY director;

Ques.2: Find the total domestic and international sales that can be attributed to each director.
Query : SELECT director,
       SUM(domestic_sales) AS total_domestic_sales,
       SUM(international_sales) AS total_international_sales
       FROM movies
       JOIN boxoffice
      ON movies.id = boxoffice.movie_id
      GROUP BY director;
